  "title": "Contributor Role Capabilities Detail",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "Contributors have all viewer capabilities and can submit proposals for new nodes, edits to existing nodes, or new/deleted edges. These proposals enter a review queue with `status = pending_admin_review` until an admin approves. A contributor may not approve their own proposals."
